properties.areaDesc: Buzzards Bay; Nantucket Sound; Vineyard Sound
properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 14 at 3:44PM EST until January 17 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Boston/Norton MA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and
seas 3 to 5 feet possible.

* WHERE...Nantucket Sound, Vineyard Sound and Buzzards Bay.

* WHEN...From Thursday morning through Friday morning.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and seas.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM THURSDAY MORNING THROUGH FRIDAY MORNING
